c: 20
v: 47
t: "“Choncho mpitireni, ndikumuuza (kuti): “Ndithu ife ndife atumiki a Mbuye wako. Asiye ana a Israyeli achoke ndi ife, ndipo usawazunze; ndithu takudzera ndi chozizwitsa chochokera kwa Mbuye wako (chomwe ndi mboni yathu pa zomwe tikukuuzazi), ndipo mtendere ukhala pa yemwe atsate chiwongoko.”"